      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/tarbera\">@Tarbera</a> ,</p>\n<p>Welcome to the <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> Community!</p>\n<p>I think you could accomplish this by setting up 2 automations.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create a column for Completed Date. Then create an automation  - example below.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/0/b02c4f2660904c42eaa42c4a84208c37818a1156.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/0/b02c4f2660904c42eaa42c4a84208c37818a1156_2_690x202.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"202\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1164×341 11 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create a second automation - example below<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/1/e1f3b769a2b7b9526da4009154fe44872e6dd6c0.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/1/e1f3b769a2b7b9526da4009154fe44872e6dd6c0_2_690x223.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"223\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1191×385 14.1 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/8/f86853ff85bab7c3a129829ba1e24640afd0a3bd.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"564\" height=\"324\" /><p></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Would this accomplish what you are looking for?</p>"
